reviews.review:
I feel really bad for the people who bought this right before L4D2 released. I love Valve, but guys.. you fucked up with l4d2. You completely scammed everyone who patroned this game. To the point where I don't trust them with l4d3. I'm not gonna be buying it until I know it's not just the same game with more shit.

Luckily, servers are still frequently made and visited. L4D1 is not abandoned. So overall, which one you want entirely depends on this;
Do you prefer quality? (l4d1) or quantity? (l4d2)
